ation of the paramA column format in S4, and the absent response message fields in S3. Let me verify there aren't any critical gaps by reviewing the source material once more, particularly around the data preparation section and log verification references.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21230,"cache_read_input_tokens":18561,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21230,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"70cb6284-8dbd-42ba-92d5-3eab631d958c","uuid":"e3e786b9-f33e-48ad-8abc-ecb398cc96d5"}
